        "Create a cell signalling receptor type comparison table with rows: GPCR, receptor tyrosine kinase (RTK), nuclear receptor. Columns: ligand type (hydrophilic/hydrophobic), receptor location (plasma membrane/intracellular), second messenger produced, downstream effector, timescale of response, one specific drug that targets this receptor class."
