        "Make a signalling pathway card set: front = pathway name (GPCR-Gαs, RTK-Ras, nuclear receptor), back = ligand type, receptor location, second messenger (if any), downstream kinase, timescale, one drug that targets this pathway. Test by covering back and drawing the pathway from memory.",
