        "For distinguishing Km and Vmax in transport context: Na⁺/K⁺-ATPase has high affinity (low Km) for Na⁺ because it must maintain a steep gradient — this mirrors enzyme kinetics. Use the same 'low Km = high affinity = low price' anchor as in the enzymes lesson."
