        "Replication enzyme sequencing drill: given a diagram of a replication fork with all enzymes removed, place each enzyme (helicase, primase, DNA Pol III on leading strand, primase × 3 on lagging strand, DNA Pol III × 3 on Okazaki fragments, DNA Pol I, ligase) in the correct position. Check. Repeat from memory without the diagram.",
