        "Create a clinical conditions comparison table: condition | affected organ/structure | underlying mechanism | macronutrient most affected | key symptom | treatment. Complete rows for coeliac disease, lactose intolerance, pancreatitis, peptic ulcer, and gallstones. This table simultaneously reviews pathology and consolidates normal physiology."
