        "For the accessory gland contributions to semen: 'Seminal vesicles = Sugar (fructose); Prostate = Protein (PSA, alkaline fluid); Bulbourethral = Buffer (pre-ejaculatory neutraliser).' The three Bs of semen: Built by seminal vesicles, Buffered by prostate, Beforehand by bulbourethral.",
