        "Create a comparison table of intramembranous vs endochondral ossification. Columns: (1) tissue template; (2) examples of bones formed; (3) cell type that initiates the process; (4) first bone tissue formed; (5) final bone tissue; (6) clinical relevance. Add a third row for endochondral ossification at the growth plate specifically — noting how it differs from endochondral ossification during embryonic development."
