        "For sympathetic vs parasympathetic effects on heart: 'Sympathetic = Sprint (speeds up); Parasympathetic = Pause (slows down).' For pupils: 'Sympathetic = Scared (dilates — fight or flight dilates pupils in darkness); Parasympathetic = Peaceful (constricts — reading in sunlight).'",
